subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Who was the first Chieftain of Mewar?
question_hi: मैर के पहले सचिव कौन थे?
explanation_en:
Rao Bika Jaisi was the first Chieftain of Mewar. He ruled during the 15th century and played a significant role in the establishment of Mewar kingdom.
